snippet.textDisplay:
FINALLY ! COKE STUDIO INDIA IS BACK (after 6 years) AND HOW !

I have been eagerly waiting for Coke Studio India to come back and make some noise like its counterpart Coke Studio Pakistan is doing this season. They are just killing it with amazing music one after the other. I hope we can learn from them and do the same and come up with great content. We have amazing underrated artists in our country too that need this platform. 
Bring back some of the gems like Papon, Mooralala Marwada, Vibha Saraf and others
